{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act35side", "eventName": "太陽甩在身後", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "AS-4", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "家傳金拖鞋", "storyInfo": "集會開始前，佩佩和幫助阿斯帕齊婭的娜仁圖亞各自運用手段打通關係，都對想要的獎品勢在必得。而博物館內，阿娜特與梅捷緹克緹因博物館的營運方式有了分歧。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g4_ctizengarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_crwddiscuss_outside", "loop": "true", "channel": "bgs", "volume": 0.0}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "SoundVolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$comedy_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1492_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 14, "prop": "StopSound", "attributes": {"channel": "bgs", "fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 16, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喔，能夠在此遇到您真是我的殊榮，哈特謝普蘇特女士。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您此次帶來的新曆紀時代初期製成的拖鞋當真是令我大開眼界，想不到數百年前的古人有如此精妙的製鞋工藝。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}}, {"id": 18, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "他們竟然能鍛造出如此貼合足部曲線的鞋履，上面裝飾的蓮花紋飾，更是生動無比。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "更不用說，這隻拖鞋誕生自那場大爆炸不久後，體現了當地氣候劇烈變化的一面。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}}, {"id": 20, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只可惜，拖鞋只有一隻，不能湊成一雙，恐怕不能在比賽中奪下第一啊。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 22, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒關係，能拿個二等獎也不錯，重在參與嘛。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 24, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "也是，哈特謝普蘇特女士您貴為帕夏之女，未來更是要繼承帕夏之位，肯定不在乎這些微末榮譽。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 26, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這個……還早啦，很多事情都說不定呢。", "name": "佩佩"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 30, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但我聽聞哈特謝普蘇特女士的幼弟已經被定為史官職位的繼承者，兩個月後便要出發前往黃金之城了。", "name": "地位不凡的富商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 31, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 32, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，像哈特謝普蘇特女士這樣天資非同一般的孩子都沒能中選，可見令弟的天賦之高。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 33, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$2"}}, {"id": 34, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉……都一樣都一樣，我和他差不多啦。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#3$2"}, {"id": 35, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_177"}}, {"id": 36, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看您說的，難道成為帕夏就不需要天賦與能力了嗎？我看哈特謝普蘇特女士要是成為帕夏，也必定能為家族延續榮光。", "name": "地位不凡的富商"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_177"}, {"id": 37, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1492_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 38, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還是不一樣的，畢竟哈特謝普蘇特女士的家族是薩爾貢最為輝煌的史官家族啊。", "name": "出身高貴的學者"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1492_1#1$1"}, {"id": 39, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}}, {"id": 40, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#5$1"}, {"id": 41, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g3_menatmainstreet_river", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "馬上就輪到我們登記了，你想好了嗎？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你那麼自信地走進參賽的報名隊伍，結果身上什麼珍寶都沒有？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你覺得我走路的儀態有什麼需要改進的地方嗎？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼，算了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看來這種時候，你還是得靠我。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 63, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我是不會看著我的手下吃虧的。給我一點時間，我想想辦法。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 65, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 67, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在短跑競速賽拿過銀牌。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 69, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你想拿起那個金杯子就跑？不行。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些有錢人帶著的護衛，來頭都不小。看那個人轉身的步法就知道他在王酋的軍隊裡幹了不少年。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我在無甲格鬥中也拿了銀牌。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "搶劫？被搶的人就在現場，我們怎麼可能拿搶來的東西參賽。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還有，在祭典舞蹈大賽中，我也拿了銀牌。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你要走這條路？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，不用為難自己……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "實際上，我在十個不同的比賽項目裡獲得了十枚銀牌，並且我一直將它們帶在身邊。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——十枚銀牌？", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這些獎牌是米諾斯傳統文化的體現，也是我個人最為珍視的榮譽。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 87, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "榮譽本不該被當做可比試高低的珍奇，但情況特殊，我只有如此選擇。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "另外，娜仁圖亞，我希望你不要誤解我。我絕不會以那樣不正當的手段參與競爭，那會使我的家族蒙羞。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#10$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "之前我確實誤解你了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#11$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，我的可靠手下，我的大事業……", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，你剛剛說什麼？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒什麼。我在說你怎麼一塊金牌都沒有，難怪那麼想要那個金杯子，哈哈。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 99, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "放心，我有計劃了。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 101, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 103, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g8_sargondeluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 105, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳……", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……請問……使者引我到這裡，是為了什麼指示？", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0, "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 115, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯？沒有沒有，不是什麼指示，就是想拜託你一件事。", "name": "寶石屏風後的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 116, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "如果你看到一隻黃金拖鞋……不要給它太高的分。", "name": "寶石屏風後的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 117, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，當然也不能太低！還是要保證歷史學家的專業性！比如說，第二名的成績就剛剛好。", "name": "寶石屏風後的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 118, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "拜託啦，這對我真的很重要！", "name": "寶石屏風後的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那件展品本就具有珍貴的歷史價值，如果您主觀想要降低評分，這也不算對其他參賽者不公平。", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 121, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.7}}, {"id": 122, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "寶石屏風後的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你如果猜到了我的身分，也請幫我保密，謝謝啦。", "name": "寶石屏風後的女性"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "是，尊敬的女士。", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 128, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite"}}, {"id": 130, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……對不起。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 134, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "以前的老師們，考古行動的同僚們……我之後一定向你們好好道歉。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 135, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是……只有這一次，我絕對絕對不能輸！憑什麼大家都覺得，我已經輸給那小子了？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#8$1"}, {"id": 137, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咿呀————————！", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（捂嘴）……是我嚇到他了嗎？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 142, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 145, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g3_menatmainstreet_river", "screenadapt": "coverall", "xScale": 1.05, "yScale": 1.05}}, {"id": 147, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 151, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 153, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "記住了？複述一遍。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 155, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米、米諾斯的銀牌套組……必須高分……一定要第、第三名……", "name": "驚恐的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 157, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒錯。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別擔心，和你坐在一間屋子裡的裁判們，大部分我都見過了。他們都和我滿聊得來的，希望你也一樣。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 159, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "action": "shake", "power": 10.0, "times": 100.0, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊……帕夏大人……貪污者的絞刑架……饒過我吧……！", "name": "驚恐的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 163, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 5.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 10.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "0,-80", "duration": 0.5, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown1", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 167, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 169, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……不會吧，這就嚇得站不起來了？之前唬住保全和其他裁判的時候沒遇到這麼大的反應啊，他看到什麼幻覺了？）", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 171, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（唉，我把你扛回門口吧。難道是我一不小心源石技藝用太猛了？）", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "focus": "n"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.5}}, {"id": 175, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#12$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 177, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（等等，有腳步聲。）", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-150,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 181, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 183, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唔……這裡也沒看到那位裁判，那應該是被保全護送回會議室了吧。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我還是去忙自己的吧，太陽可不會等人啊。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 186, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 187, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-200,0", "posto": "50,0", "duration": 1.5, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0, "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.5}}, {"id": 191, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……哎呀，看看我遇到了誰？我可真是幸運。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 195, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 197, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g4_ctizengarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 204, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 206, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，您再說一遍？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，我很榮幸地通知您，您的參賽物品進入了最終階段評選。換言之，您進入了大會前三名。", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不是這句，後一句。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "稍後請隨我移步水邊，共同參與頒獎環節與將寶物沉入河中的儀式。", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "所以……你們要把我的十枚獎牌扔進河裡？", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "怎麼會呢，那太粗魯了，我們絕不敢如此冒犯河中的神靈。", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 217, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們會將寶物放在小小的莎草船上，再加上金銀珠寶作為配重。眾人將在神聖的吟詠中，注視著祭祀品緩緩下沉。", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 219, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這一條沒有寫在你們的宣傳冊上。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不好意思，其實我們寫在了選手需要簽名的參賽須知裡。集會本來的目的，便是選出最有歷史價值的寶物，以求叩響神靈之門。", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "每一年的漫灌節，都會有被青睞的幸運兒親眼目睹神靈漫步河畔的身影。", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉，這確實是我的失誤。我報名時已經接近截止時間，來不及完整閱讀數十頁的參賽須知。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 227, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這樣吧，女士。鑒於觀光客進入最後評選的情況實屬罕見，現在您有二次確認的機會。", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 228, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "您要繼續參加嗎？", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 229, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 230, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 231, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "娜仁圖亞……", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 232, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 233, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……她還沒回來。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 234, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1490_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 235, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "女士，您是想找專家諮詢嗎？我可以帶您與集會首席裁判溝通……", "name": "集會工作人員"}}, {"id": 236, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 237, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不用了，我需要的不是建議。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 238, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我確定繼續參加。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}}, {"id": 239, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 240, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 241, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 242, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 243, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g4_ctizengarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 244, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 245, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 246, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$transmission", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 247, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 248, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 249, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂？阿娜特，聽我說！你可以準備晚上的慶功宴啦！", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 250, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$1"}}, {"id": 251, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯嗯，那還用說，我絕對不會辜負你出借展品的恩情！", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#6$1"}, {"id": 252, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 253, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我保證，晚上回去之後我會當著你的面把寶石放進去，祖拜爾如果有變化，你也可以親眼看到。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 254, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你放心，祖拜爾被我保護得很好，絕不會有任何污漬和損壞。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 255, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 256, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……讓、讓他說句話？不行不行，他……被我保護起來了嘛，我怎麼可能在眾目睽睽之下把通訊器拿給他。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}, {"id": 257, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 258, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個，我們還是說點別的吧！你根本不知道我有多難！我為了保證拿到第二名，跟那些老學究裁判周旋了一上午。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#10$1"}, {"id": 259, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}}, {"id": 260, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你聽，會場裡馬上就要宣布評選結果了。等拿到那顆寶石，我要立刻回到清靜的博物館——", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#11$1"}, {"id": 261, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 262, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1", "bstart": 0.3, "bend": 0.7, "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 263, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "200,0", "posto": "0,0", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 264, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.6}}, {"id": 265, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$bodyfalldown2", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 266, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 267, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "-50,0", "duration": 0.4}}, {"id": 268, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "xstrength": 15.0, "ystrength": 15.0, "vibrato": 15.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 269, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 0.5}}, {"id": 270, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 271, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "抱歉。", "name": "娜仁圖亞"}, "figure_art": "avg_4138_narant_1#1$1"}, {"id": 272, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 273, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 274, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 275, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "posfrom": "-50,0", "posto": "-200,0", "duration": 0.8, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 276, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "m"}}, {"id": 277, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.2}}, {"id": 278, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}}, {"id": 279, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，沒關係……", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 280, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……奇怪，這裡人行道也不窄啊。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#2$1"}, {"id": 281, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 282, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 283, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 284, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 285, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 286, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g8_sargondeluxeroom", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 287, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 288, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$victorianormal_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 289, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 290, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 291, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 292, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 293, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#13$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 294, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呼，總算可以放心了。佩佩搞定寶石的事了，祖拜爾先生也沒事。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 295, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等會我們一起去喝杯飲料？", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 296, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 297, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 298, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 299, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……你怎麼欲言又止的？", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 300, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 301, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你不會想聽的。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 302, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 303, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緹緹，我想聽你的建議。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 304, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 305, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可能你會覺得很荒唐……但我覺得特展可以重新開始，把事故包裝一下。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 306, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#5$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 307, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就當是某種節目效果，換了一種更為生動……也更加活靈活現的展出方式？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 308, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#5$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 309, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "展出會活動的古屍和文物，順便提高票價？", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 310, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 311, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "差不多吧……", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 312, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 313, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你應該知道本地人一般用什麼來嚇唬愛哭的小孩吧？", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 314, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 315, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "博物館裡的展品奇怪一點不會有問題的！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 316, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#3$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 317, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我待過的哥倫比亞的博物館就有“如果成功了會比失敗更恐怖的科技創意展覽”。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 318, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 319, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可是緹緹，那種以賺錢為第一目標的商業化營運想法，在這裡會惹很多人生氣，很多很多人。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 320, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座城市的立身之本可是歷史！", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 321, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 322, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這座城市的立身之本難道不是那條快要枯竭的寶石礦脈嗎？", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 323, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 324, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……等一下我們去見那些貴族的時候千萬別這麼說。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 325, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那個家族幾乎和博物館大廳那塊陵墓的石磚一樣古老，而且保守。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 326, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 327, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "為什麼我們有那麼多王酋、帕夏們總是愛管這管那！他們就不能像佩佩的家族一樣每年按時打筆鉅款，然後對這裡的一切不聞不問嗎！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 328, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 329, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緹緹，代理館長的機會來之不易，我真的不想惹上什麼麻煩。", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 330, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 331, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "麻煩……你居然把這當麻煩！", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 332, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 333, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我也不是這個意思……", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 334, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1478_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 335, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……那就按你說的來吧，我先走了。", "name": "梅捷緹克緹"}}, {"id": 336, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 337, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_walkfast", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 338, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "posfrom": "0,0", "posto": "150,0", "duration": 1.0, "afrom": 1.0, "ato": 0.0}}, {"id": 339, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 340, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$doorclosequite", "volume": 1.0}}, {"id": 341, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 342, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_4139_papyrs_1#9$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 343, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "緹緹，我……", "name": "阿娜特"}}, {"id": 344, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 345, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 346, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 347, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 348, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 349, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "53_g4_ctizengarden", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 350, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 351, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$holiday_intro", "key": "$holiday_loop", "volume": 0.6}}, {"id": 352, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause"}}, {"id": 353, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 354, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 355, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 356, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 357, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 358, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（您還好嗎？我看您滿頭大汗……）", "name": "嚴謹的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 359, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 360, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（是、是嗎？……今天室外太熱了，哈哈，您也在流汗啊……）", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 361, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 362, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 363, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "接下來是輝煌的史官家族傳人、王者與英雄的傳頌者、足跡遍布薩爾貢的探險家、博聞之人、尊貴的帕夏之女——", "name": "集會主持人"}}, {"id": 364, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哈特謝普蘇特女士為我們帶來的珍奇寶物！", "name": "集會主持人"}}, {"id": 365, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "name": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 366, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "right", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 367, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（那……這個結果，您來宣布？）", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 368, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "left", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 369, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（不，這麼重要的機會，還是請您來吧。）", "name": "嚴謹的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 370, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 371, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "（……哈哈，那我不敢再推辭了。）", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}}, {"id": 372, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 373, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 374, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_mictest", "volume": 0.7}}, {"id": 375, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 376, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 377, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "咳咳……", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 378, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，這隻黃金拖鞋上有金絲編織的蓮花，並根據當時急劇變化的薩爾貢氣候進行了特殊設計，有著非常清晰的時代特徵。", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 379, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且，它來自聲名顯赫的帝國史官家族。", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 380, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們很難在市面上看到保存如此完整的，且與史官家族風格不符的日用品——", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 381, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "在以往的集會中，從史官家族流出的大多是書信、文稿等藏品。", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 382, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 383, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而今天，這隻拖鞋，它向我們展示了貴族在那個時代生活的另一個側面，它的價值不可估量！", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 384, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 385, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，謝謝您的點評。接下來我將公布裁判席評分。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 386, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "集會主持人", "content": "去掉一個最高分，去掉一個最低分，哈特謝普蘇特女士的最終得分是"}}, {"id": 387, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 388, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause"}}, {"id": 389, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "集會主持人", "content": " ——94.95分。"}}, {"id": 390, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀……抱歉，尊敬的哈特謝普蘇特女士，您以0.05分之差，暫時位居第二……", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 391, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 392, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這是我們基於公正的原則和對歷史的尊重得出的結果，請您諒解，哈特謝普蘇特女士。", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 393, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#10$1"}}, {"id": 394, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事沒事，和我的預期一樣，嘿嘿。", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#10$1"}, {"id": 395, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 396, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "米納特哈瑪儀很榮幸能接受您的考驗……我、我們還是進入下一件吧。", "name": "緊張的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 397, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 398, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，下一件，也是本次大會的最後一件參賽展品……", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 399, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……來自異域的珍寶，米諾斯的銀牌套組。有請我們的專家做出評價。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1494_1#1$1"}, {"id": 400, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 401, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們都知道……薩爾貢邊遠的地區同樣有著璀璨的文明，米諾斯地區的一些文化藝術也能很好地與薩爾貢的風俗融合。", "name": "嚴謹的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1"}, {"id": 402, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這套銀牌不僅體現了米諾斯人熱愛體育運動的傳統，更重要的是，和大多數參賽展品相比，它的製成年份能被尤為精確地判定。", "name": "嚴謹的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1"}, {"id": 403, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "而且……眾所周知，我們的生活中充滿了金製品，但銀製品卻是很少見的。", "name": "嚴謹的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1"}, {"id": 404, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "事實上，在一些歷史階段中，銀確實比金更加珍貴。", "name": "嚴謹的集會裁判"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1"}, {"id": 405, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 406, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常有趣的點評！那麼，最終究竟會是哪三位選手獲得代表城市祭祀河流的機會呢？請允許我為大家揭曉這一寶物獲得的評分……", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1"}, {"id": 407, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "集會主持人", "content": "去掉一個最高分，去掉一個最低分，來自米諾斯的阿斯帕齊婭女士最終得分是"}}, {"id": 408, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_applause"}}, {"id": 409, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 410, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "集會主持人", "content": "——94.60分。"}}, {"id": 411, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這真是前所未有的激烈競爭！阿斯帕齊婭女士，您最終位列第三，雖然有些遺憾，但您也獲得了祭祀的機會。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1495_1#1$1"}, {"id": 412, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 413, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "非常感謝，這正是我需要的認可。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 414, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是，如果你們允許的話，大會結束後我要向你們抗議獎項設置的問題。我認為米諾斯的金杯不該只是三等獎獎品。", "name": "阿斯帕齊婭"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 415, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 416, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好的，女士，但請您先到台上來，拿上您的展品，跟隨工作人員的指引。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 417, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 418, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 419, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 420, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第三名，阿斯帕齊婭女士。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1477_1#1$1"}, {"id": 421, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 422, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 423, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 424, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 425, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第二名，哈特謝普蘇特女士。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#1$1"}, {"id": 426, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 427, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 428, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1", "duration": 1.0}}, {"id": 429, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 430, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "第一名，拉沙德女士。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 431, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 432, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三位獲獎選手，請小心不要損壞手中的展品……", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 433, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 434, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_ceramicrack"}}, {"id": 435, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 0.3, "xstrength": 30.0, "ystrength": 30.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 436, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 437, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 438, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哎呀——！", "name": "拉沙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 439, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真不好意思，天氣太熱，我有些虛脫……一時沒拿穩手裡的東西，讓各位見笑了。", "name": "拉沙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 440, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，可惜我拿來的這件古陶罐摔碎了。我想，用碎片祭祀河流恐怕是不行的吧？", "name": "拉沙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 441, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 442, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這……從未有過先例……", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 443, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 444, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "真讓人傷心啊……我恐怕只能放棄這個第一了。", "name": "拉沙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 445, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不過，尊敬的帕夏之女，哈特謝普蘇特女士，這會場裡本就不該有比您名次更高的人，這第一給您才是實至名歸。", "name": "拉沙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 446, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "就這樣吧，我自願放棄我的名次，退出比賽。", "name": "拉沙德"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_1491_1#1$1"}, {"id": 447, "prop": "Effect", "attributes": {"name": "$e_emoji_blackline", "layer": 1.0, "x": 50.0, "y": 180.0}}, {"id": 448, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}}, {"id": 449, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "……啊？", "name": "佩佩"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 450, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 451, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃……場上出現了意外情況！但我相信，在場所有人都認同，我們尊敬的帕夏之女應該獲得大會頭名！", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 452, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那麼，獲得二至四名的選手將順次獲得我們的一二三等獎。", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 453, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "讓我們祝賀他們！", "name": "集會主持人"}, "figure_art": "avg_4058_pepe_1#12$1"}, {"id": 454, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 455, "prop": "CameraShake", "attributes": {"duration": 2.0, "xstrength": 10.0, "ystrength": 10.0, "vibrato": 30.0, "randomness": 90.0, "fadeout": "true", "block": "false"}}, {"id": 456, "prop": "PlaySound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_avg_cheer_street"}}, {"id": 457, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 458, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 459, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 460, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 461, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 462, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 463, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 464, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}